{\displaystyle \partial _{\mu }\left({\frac {\partial {\mathcal {L}}}{\partial (\partial _{\mu }\psi )}}\right)-{\frac {\partial {\mathcal {L}}}{\partial \psi }}=0\quad \quad \quad \quad \quad \quad \quad \quad \quad \quad \quad \quad (2)\,}



