□ 物理實驗能力
 
□ 研究導向物理知識
 
 

課程概述 Course Description
       電動力學和量子力學為高等物理的基礎科目, 研究生一年級的必修課. 學生修習本科目必須學會
1. 靜電和靜磁的基本定律,
2. Ｐoisson 方程式在幾種邊界條件的解法, 包括直角坐標系, 圓柱座標系, 和圓座標系.
3. 電磁波理論和 Maxwell 方程式
4. 介電材料電磁波理論
5. 波傳導, 反射與折射
6. 波導管, 和輻射理論. (1)	Introduction.
(2)	Special Relativity and Covariant Form of Electromagnetic Field.
(3)	Brief Discussion on Radiation.
(4)	Solutions of Static EM fields

    

課程學習目標 Course Objectives
The generalized methods in electrostaticsThe generalized methods in magentostaticsThe generalized methods in Maxwell's equations 

課程進度 Course Outline


週次 Week進度說明 Progress Description
1Introduction to electrostatics2Introduction to electrostatics3Boundary-value problems in electrostatics I4Boundary-value problems in electrostatics I5Boundary-value problems in electrostatics II6Boundary-value problems in electrostatics II7Boundary-value problems in electrostatics II8Boundary-value problems in electrostatics II9Midterm exam10Multipoles,electrostatics of macroscopic media,dielectrics11Multipoles,electrostatics of macroscopic media,dielectrics12Magentostatics,Faraday's law, quasi-static fields13Magentostatics,Faraday's law, quasi-static fields14Magentostatics,Faraday's law, quasi-static fields15Maxwell equations,plane electromagnetic waves16Maxwell equations,plane electromagnetic waves17Maxwell equations,plane electromagnetic waves18Final exam 

　以上每週進度教師可依上課情況做適度調整。The schedule may be subject to change.


